<Configuration>
  <!-- Windows Sandbox config pentru testare robOS ca student fresh.
       Double-click pe acest fisier deschide un sandbox cu:
       - Folder licensing/build/ mapat read-only la C:\Users\WDAGUtilityAccount\Desktop\robos-build
         (asa ai tarball-ul gata, fara download)
       - Clipboard partajat (poti copia comenzi din host in sandbox)
       - Network activ (pentru install Node, Claude, npm install, license bind)

       Cum folosesti:
       1. Activeaza Windows Sandbox (Windows Pro/Enterprise/Education):
          Settings → Apps → Optional features → "Windows Sandbox" enable
          (sau PowerShell admin: Enable-WindowsOptionalFeature -Online -FeatureName "Containers-DisposableClientVM" -All)
       2. Restart laptop
       3. Double-click pe acest fisier (.wsb) → Sandbox porneste in ~5 secunde
       4. In Sandbox, deschide folder "robos-build" de pe Desktop, apoi
          DOUBLE-CLICK pe "open-powershell.cmd" → se deschide PowerShell + STEPS.txt
          in Notepad cu pasii de install. Copy-paste pas cu pas.

       Pasi student fresh in sandbox (DETALIAT in STEPS.txt din folder-ul mapat;
       reproducere mai jos pentru context, dar STEPS.txt e sursa de adevar):

       IMPORTANT: Windows Sandbox NU vine cu winget pre-instalat (limitare
       cunoscuta — Sandbox e Windows fara Microsoft Store). Pe Windows real,
       winget functioneaza si comanda din welcomeEmail merge. In sandbox,
       folosesti download direct sub:

       a. Install Node.js (download .msi direct):
          # IMPORTANT: foloseste >= v22.12.0 (Astro cere asta — robOS dashboard
          # build esueaza pe v22.11.0 cu "Node.js is not supported by Astro").
          $url = "https://nodejs.org/dist/v22.12.0/node-v22.12.0-x64.msi"
          $out = "$env:TEMP\node.msi"
          Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $url -OutFile $out
          Start-Process msiexec.exe -ArgumentList "/i `"$out`" /qn /norestart" -Wait
          exit  # Inchide PowerShell pentru PATH refresh

       b. (PowerShell NOU) Install Claude Code:
           Set-ExecutionPolicy -Scope Process -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Force
           $s = irm https://claude.ai/install.ps1
           & ([scriptblock]::Create($s))
           $env:Path += ";$env:USERPROFILE\.local\bin"

       c. Install VSCode (silent, cu addtopath ca robos sa il detecteze):
          $url = "https://code.visualstudio.com/sha/download?build=stable&os=win32-x64-user"
          $out = "$env:TEMP\vscode.exe"
          Invoke-WebRequest -Uri $url -OutFile $out
          Start-Process $out -ArgumentList "/VERYSILENT","/MERGETASKS=!runcode,addtopath" -Wait
          exit  # PATH refresh

       d. (PowerShell NOU) Extract + lansare robOS:
          $env:Path += ";$env:USERPROFILE\.local\bin"
          mkdir C:\robos -Force
          cd C:\robos
          tar -xzf "C:\Users\WDAGUtilityAccount\Desktop\robos-build\robos-base-v0.5.1.tar.gz"
          cd robOS
          .\scripts\robos.cmd

       e. Astepti: VSCode se deschide automat cu folderul robOS, dashboard
          la localhost:3001. In VSCode: View → Terminal → claude → "onboard me".

       Cleanup: inchide fereastra sandbox-ului → totul dispare. Reset complet.
  -->

  <MappedFolders>
    <MappedFolder>
      <HostFolder>C:\claude_os\robos\licensing\build</HostFolder>
      <SandboxFolder>C:\Users\WDAGUtilityAccount\Desktop\robos-build</SandboxFolder>
      <ReadOnly>true</ReadOnly>
    </MappedFolder>
  </MappedFolders>

  <ClipboardRedirection>true</ClipboardRedirection>
  <Networking>Default</Networking>
  <AudioInput>Disable</AudioInput>
  <VideoInput>Disable</VideoInput>
  <ProtectedClient>Enable</ProtectedClient>

  <!-- 8 GB RAM (default sandbox = 4 GB). Claude install + npm install +
       astro build cer mai mult — cu 4 GB primesti 'Out of memory' la Claude. -->
  <MemoryInMB>8192</MemoryInMB>
</Configuration>
